		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have some spare connectors in my stash. Did you try cleaning it? I doubt you've damaged anything, but you should try bypassing the fuse with a small length of wire to check if it's faulty. 
<br />
<br />If the slot is dirty/corroded, then it may not be making a solid enough connection tot he games. In fact, clean the carts too! The FC will display a black or purple screen if 'tisn't getting a good signal from the ROM/Mapper (amongst other reasons).

		

